member.name: P:MisSchoolWeb.Resources.rsMain.checkUser
member.summary: Looks up a localized string similar to SELECT u.UserName AS [iUser] ,U.[Password],IsNull(th.Fname,'') + ' ' + IsNull(th.Lname,'') AS UserName, IsNull(tp.PrefixNameFull,'') + IsNull(th.Fname,'') + ' ' + IsNull(th.Lname,'') AS UserNameFull, u.TeacherNo FROM Personal.dbo.tblUserName AS U LEFT JOIN Personal.dbo.tblTeacherHis AS TH ON u.TeacherNo = th.TeacherNo LEFT JOIN BaseData.dbo.tblPrefix AS tp ON th.PrefixNo = tp.PrefixNo WHERE [username] = '{0}' AND U.[Password] = '{1}'.

member.name: P:MisSchoolWeb.Resources.rsMain.strConn
member.summary: Looks up a localized string similar to Data Source=.\sqlexpress;Initial Catalog=Tabain;Persist Security Info=True;User ID=sa;Password=mengae.

member.name: P:MisSchoolWeb.Resources.rsMain.Student
member.summary: Looks up a localized string similar to SELECT tsr.No_Room,tsr.StdNo, ts.Fname , ts.Lname FROM Tabain.dbo.tblStudentRoom AS tsr LEFT JOIN Tabain.dbo.tblStudentNumber SN ON tsr.StdNo = sn.StdNo LEFT JOIN Tabain.dbo.tblStudent AS ts ON sn.StdNoRef = ts.StdNoRef LEFT JOIN BaseData.dbo.tblPrefix AS tp ON ts.PreFixNo = tp.PrefixNo WHERE tsr.LavelNo + tsr.DepartNo + tsr.RoundNo + tsr.[Year] + tsr.Room = '{0}' Order BY No_Room,tsr.StdNo.

member.name: P:MisSchoolWeb.Resources.rsMain.StudentDel
member.summary: Looks up a localized string similar to DELETE FROM Tabain.dbo.tblStudent WHERE stdnoref IN (SELECT StdNoRef FROM Tabain.dbo.tblStudentNumber AS tsn WHERE stdno = @p1 ).

member.name: P:MisSchoolWeb.Resources.rsMain.StudentRoom
member.summary: Looks up a localized string similar to SELECT tsr.No_Room,tsr.StdNo, tp.PrefixNameFull + ts.Fname + ' ' + ts.Lname AS StdName ,tp.PrefixNameFullEng + ts.FNameEng + ' ' + ts.LNameEng AS StdNameEng FROM Tabain.dbo.tblStudentRoom AS tsr LEFT JOIN Tabain.dbo.tblStudentNumber SN ON tsr.StdNo = sn.StdNo LEFT JOIN Tabain.dbo.tblStudent AS ts ON sn.StdNoRef = ts.StdNoRef LEFT JOIN BaseData.dbo.tblPrefix AS tp ON ts.PreFixNo = tp.PrefixNo WHERE tsr.LavelNo + tsr.DepartNo + tsr.RoundNo + tsr.[Year] + tsr.Room = '{0}' Order BY No_Room,tsr.StdNo.

member.name: P:MisSchoolWeb.Resources.rsMain.StudentUpdate
member.summary: Looks up a localized string similar to Update Tabain.Dbo.tblStudent SET Fname = @p1, Lname = @p2 From _Tabain.Dbo.tblStudent TS LEFT JOIN _Tabain.Dbo.tblStudentNumber TN ON TS.StdNoRef = TN.StdNoRef Where TN.StdNo = @p3.
